text:
Wow... just like we saw on Twesta,
this is such a lovely shop...

Hehe, thanks to you, Haruki-chan,
I get to visit all sorts of fun shops.

Yeah!
I wouldn't be able to find places like this on my own.

Well then, I should research more
nice shops for Hana-chan too.

...But, in that case,

Hehe~. Then I'll be really happy if you enjoy
the seasonal limited menu we're about to receive!
